"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-02-24-2024-olympic-qualifier-we-can-beat-super-falcons-cameroon-coach-bisseck\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  The Indomitable Lionesses of Cameroon head coach, Jean-Baptiste Bisseck believes his side still has a decent chance of making it to the final round of the 2024 Olympic Games Qualifier.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lionesses were held to a 0-0 draw by fierce rivals Nigeria in the first leg of their third-round tie in Douala on Friday.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 260, \"end\": 267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9684437977115958, \"rank\": 0.03001077104467726, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douala\", \"score\": 0.9999999999481588, \"rank\": 3.7654860016866046e-11, \"text\": \"Douala\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douala\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hosts carved out a number of chances in the game but were frustrated by Super Falcons goalkeeper, Chiamaka Nnadozie, who was at her imperious best.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiamaka_Nnadozie\", \"score\": 1